{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6",
    "translationId": "rsv",
    "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
    "chapterNumber": 6,
    "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6",
    "summary": "Source text for 1 Chronicles 6 in Revised Standard Version."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.1",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:1",
      "text": "The sons of Levi: Gershom, Kohath, and Merari.",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.2",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:2",
      "text": "The sons of Kohath: Amram, Izhar, Hebron, and Uzziel.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.3",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:3",
      "text": "The children of Amram: Aaron, Moses, and Miriam. The sons of Aaron: Nadab, Abihu, Eleazar, and Ithamar.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.4",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:4",
      "text": "Eleazar was the father of Phinehas, Phinehas of Abishua,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.5",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:5",
      "text": "Abishua of Bukki, Bukki of Uzzi,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.6",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:6",
      "text": "Uzzi of Zerahiah, Zerahiah of Meraioth,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.7",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:7",
      "text": "Meraioth of Amariah, Amariah of Ahitub,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.8",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:8",
      "text": "Ahitub of Zadok, Zadok of Ahima-az,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.9",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:9",
      "text": "Ahima-az of Azariah, Azariah of Johanan,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.10",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:10",
      "text": "and Johanan of Azariah (it was he who served as priest in the house that Solomon built in Jerusalem).",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.11",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:11",
      "text": "Azariah was the father of Amariah, Amariah of Ahitub,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.12",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:12",
      "text": "Ahitub of Zadok, Zadok of Shallum,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.13",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:13",
      "text": "Shallum of Hilkiah, Hilkiah of Azariah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.14",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:14",
      "text": "Azariah of Seraiah, Seraiah of Jehozadak;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.15",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:15",
      "text": "and Jehozadak went into exile when the Lord sent Judah and Jerusalem into exile by the hand of Nebuchadnezzar.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.16",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:16",
      "text": "The sons of Levi: Gershom, Kohath, and Merari.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.17",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:17",
      "text": "And these are the names of the sons of Gershom: Libni and Shime-i.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.18",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:18",
      "text": "The sons of Kohath: Amram, Izhar, Hebron, and Uzziel.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.19",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:19",
      "text": "The sons of Merari: Mahli and Mushi. These are the families of the Levites according to their fathers.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.20",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:20",
      "text": "Of Gershom: Libni his son, Jahath his son, Zimmah his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.21",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:21",
      "text": "Joah his son, Iddo his son, Zerah his son, Je-atherai his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.22",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:22",
      "text": "The sons of Kohath: Amminadab his son, Korah his son, Assir his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.23",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:23",
      "text": "Elkanah his son, Ebiasaph his son, Assir his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.24",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:24",
      "text": "Tahath his son, Uriel his son, Uzziah his son, and Shaul his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.25",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:25",
      "text": "The sons of Elkanah: Amasai and Ahimoth,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.26",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:26",
      "text": "Elkanah his son, Zophai his son, Nahath his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.27",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:27",
      "text": "Eliab his son, Jeroham his son, Elkanah his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.28",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:28",
      "text": "The sons of Samuel: Joel his first-born, the second Abijah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.29",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:29",
      "text": "The sons of Merari: Mahli, Libni his son, Shime-i his son, Uzzah his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.30",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:30",
      "text": "Shime-a his son, Haggiah his son, and Asaiah his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.31",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:31",
      "text": "These are the men whom David put in charge of the service of song in the house of the Lord, after the ark rested there.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.32",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:32",
      "text": "They ministered with song before the tabernacle of the tent of meeting, until Solomon had built the house of the Lord in Jerusalem; and they performed their service in due order.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.33",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 33,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:33",
      "text": "These are the men who served and their sons. Of the sons of the Kohathites: Heman the singer the son of Joel, son of Samuel,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.34",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 34,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:34",
      "text": "son of Elkanah, son of Jeroham, son of Eliel, son of Toah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.35",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:35",
      "text": "son of Zuph, son of Elkanah, son of Mahath, son of Amasai,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.36",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 36,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:36",
      "text": "son of Elkanah, son of Joel, son of Azariah, son of Zephaniah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.37",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 37,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:37",
      "text": "son of Tahath, son of Assir, son of Ebiasaph, son of Korah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.38",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 38,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:38",
      "text": "son of Izhar, son of Kohath, son of Levi, son of Israel;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.39",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 39,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:39",
      "text": "and his brother Asaph, who stood on his right hand, namely, Asaph the son of Berechiah, son of Shime-a,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.40",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 40,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:40",
      "text": "son of Michael, son of Ba-aseiah, son of Malchijah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.41",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 41,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:41",
      "text": "son of Ethni, son of Zerah, son of Adaiah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.42",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 42,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:42",
      "text": "son of Ethan, son of Zimmah, son of Shime-i,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.43",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 43,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:43",
      "text": "son of Jahath, son of Gershom, son of Levi.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.44",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 44,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:44",
      "text": "On the left hand were their brethren the sons of Merari: Ethan the son of Kishi, son of Abdi, son of Malluch,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.45",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 45,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:45",
      "text": "son of Hashabiah, son of Amaziah, son of Hilkiah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.46",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 46,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:46",
      "text": "son of Amzi, son of Bani, son of Shemer,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.47",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 47,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:47",
      "text": "son of Mahli, son of Mushi, son of Merari, son of Levi;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.48",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 48,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:48",
      "text": "and their brethren the Levites were appointed for all the service of the tabernacle of the house of God.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.49",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 49,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:49",
      "text": "But Aaron and his sons made offerings upon the altar of burnt offering and upon the altar of incense for all the work of the most holy place, and to make atonement for Israel, according to all that Moses the servant of God had commanded.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.50",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 50,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:50",
      "text": "These are the sons of Aaron: Eleazar his son, Phinehas his son, Abishua his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.51",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 51,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:51",
      "text": "Bukki his son, Uzzi his son, Zerahiah his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.52",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 52,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:52",
      "text": "Meraioth his son, Amariah his son, Ahitub his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.53",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 53,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:53",
      "text": "Zadok his son, Ahima-az his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.54",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 54,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:54",
      "text": "These are their dwelling places according to their settlements within their borders: to the sons of Aaron of the families of Kohathites, for theirs was the lot,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.55",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 55,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:55",
      "text": "to them they gave Hebron in the land of Judah and its surrounding pasture lands,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.56",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 56,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:56",
      "text": "but the fields of the city and its villages they gave to Caleb the son of Jephunneh.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.57",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 57,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:57",
      "text": "To the sons of Aaron they gave the cities of refuge: Hebron, Libnah with its pasture lands, Jattir, Eshtemoa with its pasture lands,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.58",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 58,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:58",
      "text": "Hilen with its pasture lands, Debir with its pasture lands,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.59",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 59,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:59",
      "text": "Ashan with its pasture lands, and Beth-shemesh with its pasture lands;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.60",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 60,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:60",
      "text": "and from the tribe of Benjamin, Geba with its pasture lands, Alemeth with its pasture lands, and Anathoth with its pasture lands. All their cities throughout their families were thirteen.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.61",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 61,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:61",
      "text": "To the rest of the Kohathites were given by lot out of the family of the tribe, out of the half-tribe, the half of Manasseh, ten cities.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.62",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 62,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:62",
      "text": "To the Gershomites according to their families were allotted thirteen cities out of the tribes of Issachar, Asher, Naphtali, and Manasseh in Bashan.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.63",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 63,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:63",
      "text": "To the Merarites according to their families were allotted twelve cities out of the tribes of Reuben, Gad, and Zebulun.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.64",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 64,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:64",
      "text": "So the people of Israel gave the Levites the cities with their pasture lands.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.6.65",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 6,
      "verseNumber": 65,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 6:65",
